#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdso-integration-phase-plan.md:65
msgid "Known DSO API quirks"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdso-integration-phase-plan.md:67
msgid ""
"**Opvragen Werkzaamheden `_expandScope`:** the spec documents "
"`logischeRelaties` as the valid enum value but the runtime rejects both "
"`logischeRelaties` and `LogischeRelaties`. `_expand=true` without "
"`_expandScope` is also rejected. Current workaround: call without expand — "
"returns version history with omschrijving and dates only. Keywords and "
"logical relations pending until the correct enum value is confirmed with DSO "
"support."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdso-integration-phase-plan.md:68
msgid ""
"**RTR `_wijzigingen`:** is a **delta sync endpoint**, not a browse endpoint. "
"It returns activities that changed since `datumVanaf`, not activities valid "
"on a date. Empty results for recent dates are expected if nothing changed. "
"Replaced by `POST /activiteiten/_zoek` with `bestuursorgaan.oin` for all OIN-"
"based browsing in LDE."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdso-integration-phase-plan.md:69
msgid ""
"**Manual date format:** `dd-MM-yyyy` throughout — no `Intl` dependency due "
"to Azure App Service locale issues."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdso-integration-phase-plan.md:70
msgid ""
"**`functioneleStructuurRef` format:** two variants exist (see above). The "
"authority-scoped RTR detail format is needed for the Uitvoeren Gegevens "
"lookup in Phase 4."
msgstr ""

